<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/portfolio/student/show.css">
    <title>Asparsh | Portfolio</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="user-logo">
            <a href="/"><p>Asparsh</p></a>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <input type="checkbox" id="menu-toggle" class="menu-toggle" />
            <label for="menu-toggle" class="menu-icon">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            </label>
            <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/show">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/blog">Blog</a></li>
            <li><a href="/portfolio/student/contact" class="contact-link">Contact Me</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="portfolio-hero">
            <div class="portfolio-contents">
                <h2>Hello, I'm a Student</h2>
                <h1>My name is John Doe</h1>
                <p>I am a passionate web developer. I have experience in building responsive websites and web applications. Apart from that, I enjoy learning new technologies and improving my skills. My hobbies include hiking, photography, and playing the guitar.</p>
                <div class="portfolio-contact">
                    <a href="/portfolio/student/contact" class="contact-button">Contact Me</a>
                    <a href="/portfolio/edit" class="edit-button">My  Portfolio</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="portfolio-image">
                <img src="/assets/portfolio-image.jpg" alt="Portfolio Image">
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="portfolio-biography">
            <div class="biography-image">
                <img src="/assets/biography-image.jpg" alt="Biography Image">
            </div>
            <div class="biography-content">
                <h3>My Biography</h3>
                <h2>A lead web developer with a passion for creating dynamic and responsive web applications.</h2>
                <p>I am a student with a keen interest in web development. I have worked on several projects that showcase my skills in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I am always eager to learn new technologies and improve my coding skills. My goal is to become a full-stack developer and contribute to open-source projects.</p>
                <div class="quick-info">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Age</h4>
                        <p>20</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Location</h4>
                        <p>New York, USA</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Email</h4>
                        <p>tempmail@example.com</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <h4>Phone</h4>
                        <p>+1 234 567 890</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="follow-me">
                    Follow me on:
                    <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        GitHub
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        LinkedIn
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        Twitter
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        Instagram
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" class="social-link">
                        Facebook
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-me">
                    <button onclick="window.location.href='/portfolio/student/contact'" class="hire-me">Hire Me</button>
                    <a href="/assets/cv.pdf" class="download-cv" download>
                        <button type="button">Download CV</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>